2.title: Rattlesnake in My Car
2.plot: It's man versus reptile - and it's not just a fight, it's outright war. A rattlesnake goes swimming in a woman's pool while another is hiding in the depths of a woman's car, waiting to strike.

5.title: Deadly Reptile Mix
5.plot: An alligator blocking a roadway tries to rip off Lt. Lisa Wood's leg. A deadly rattlesnake strikes out from underneath thick brush, and when the Venom One team gets called out to a dog rescue, they find not one, but three killer snakes.

6.title: Foreign Invasion
6.plot: Chuck & Ernie have captured every deadly reptile in the Everglades, so now they venture to Costa Rica for the ultimate snakation, all in search of the largest pit viper ever, the Black Headed Bushmaster.

1.title: Killer Pythons
1.plot: Ever since Hurricane Andrew destroyed a snake breeding facility, pythons have been multiplying in the Everglades. The Venom One team hunts down many of these dangerous constrictors, including a giant 14-foot python that is roaming the streets of Miami.

2.title: Cannibal Gator
2.plot: Gators turn up everywhere, from backyard pools to guest bathrooms - one woman is even killed by a gator while gardening. And when beheaded pythons start turning up in Miami, could a mystical religion that practices animal sacrifice be at work.

3.title: Gator vs. Python
3.plot: After a python eats a gator, theories on the battle between the two run rampant. African Rock pythons are now becoming a big problem in the suburbs of Miami. They are breeding fast and are far more aggressive and deadlier than their Burmese counterparts.

4.title: Snake Farm Shootout
4.plot: Keeping your children safe is the top responsibility for all parents. In South Florida, where killer reptiles roam free, that's increasingly hard to do. A venomous coral snake strikes a child and sends him into a coma.

5.title: Snakes Attack Suburbia
5.plot: Burmese pythons continue to multiply and are creeping into unexpected places. Venomous cottonmouths are also turning up, even in a playground. When a teenage boy is bit by one of these deadly snakes, the Venom 1 team must rush into action with anti-venom.

6.title: Killer in Your Mailbox
6.plot: Be careful sticking your hand in the mailbox, because the deadliest snake in North America could be waiting to bite. Plus Capt. Seifert must capture a 12-foot python with amazing speed and agility, and when Capt. Fobb closes in on another python.

7.title: A Python Ate My Pet
7.plot: Pythons are pushing out into people's yards, killing and consuming any animals in their path. When a python is captured with a meal in its stomach, the Venom One team must find out if someone's pet is inside.

8.title: Hurricane: Gator Lockdown
8.plot:
Know what this is about?
 Be the first one to add a plot.

9.title: Killer Bees Attack
9.plot: Killer bees are spreading across the southern U.S. These angry and aggressive bees attack by the thousands, sometimes stinging their victims to death. When a man is trapped inside his home with killer bees, the Venom One team needs to get him to safety.

10.title: Flesh-Eating Lizards
10.plot: Florida is faced with a new invasion - African Nile monitor lizards. These carnivorous lizards are moving into new areas and brazenly entering people's yards and patios. They will eat almost anything in their path, even people.

11.title: Deer-Eating Python
11.plot: A monstrous Burmese python is lurking near a daycare, and these pythons from the swamp are capable of devouring a meal the size of a twelve-year-old. And extracting venom from the deadly King Cobra could save lives, but it could also quickly claim them.

12.title: Monsters in the Backyard
12.plot: Monsters have become so prolific in the Everglades, that lawmakers have banned imports of several large constrictors, but it may be too late, because it didn't stop a 13-foot killer python from taking a dip in a neighborhood pool - on Christmas morning.

13.title: Florida's Born Killers
13.plot: A families' escaped pet python kills their young daughter. Chuck searches the Everglades for a nasty Burmese python. Ernie must tear apart fences to capture an aggressive red tail boa loose in a suburban neighborhood.

-1.title: Hurricane Gator Lockdown
-1.plot: As a giant hurricane rapidly approaches the coast of South Florida, the Venom One team races to lockdown a 400 pound gator, angry crocodiles and venomous snakes. If they're not secured properly, the hurricane could release them into the streets of Miami.

imdb.plot outline: When it comes to the planet's most venomous creatures, only one team has the knowledge & courage to battle them, the Venom One Response Team. Follow this elite unit of specially trained emergency response paramedics, currently holding the largest & only anti-venom bank open to the public, as they race against time to capture these killer reptiles and deliver anti-venom to their victims, ultimately their saving lives.
